    {
      "chinese": "泰雅民族（gluw na Tayal Minzok）的起源，有說源自發祥瑞岩（Pinsbkan）；有說源自大霸尖山（Papak Waqa）；也有部份的家族聲稱來自苗栗（Bari）、台中（Thetun）海邊；亦有說曾經居於山下的埔里（Tlisi）。",
      "ab": "puqing inringan balay gluw na Tayal Minzok ga, kya qu kmayal mha minkahul sami Pinsbkan, maki ku kmayal mha kahul sami Papak Waqa, maki uzi qu qutux glgluw ga kmayal mha kahul sami Bari, Thetun ka syaw na bsilung, kruma ga kmayal mha kahul sami te hugan ka Tlisi.",
      "order": "2",
      "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2021/03/12/39bd583ce11d1cd02526eb25c19bdee9.wav",
